A Nigerian man has landed in serious trouble after killing his 6-month-old daughter just to get back at his wife for dumping him. The sad incident took place in Abaomege, Ebonyi state. The suspect, identified as Sunday Anthony, buried the girl in a shallow grave he dug at the back of his house, yesterday, shortly after his wife packed out. Luck, however, ran out on him as he was caught later in the day. Watch video below : Source